# FreeRADIUS Custom Dictionary
# Includes MikroTik and WISPr vendor attributes for bandwidth control

# WISPr attributes (RFC standard)
ATTRIBUTE WISPr-Bandwidth-Max-Up         16  integer
ATTRIBUTE WISPr-Bandwidth-Max-Down       17  integer

# MikroTik vendor-specific attributes
VENDOR Mikrotik 14988
BEGIN-VENDOR Mikrotik
ATTRIBUTE Mikrotik-Rate-Limit            15  string
END-VENDOR Mikrotik
